 what they're about.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-16-test-2-part-1-2022-12-31-23-02-16/37.mp3","time_start":114.55,"time_end":120.17},{"position":38,"content":"So can you keep them in those groups when you copy them?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-16-test-2-part-1-2022-12-31-23-02-16/38.mp3","time_start":120.31,"time_end":123.9},{"position":39,"content":"Sure.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-16-test-2-part-1-2022-12-31-23-02-16/39.mp3","time_start":124.13,"time_end":125.09},{"position":40,"content":"We'll save each group in a different folder on the disk and if you like, you can suggest a name for each folder.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-16-test-2-part-1-2022-12-31-23-02-16/40.mp3","time_start":125.18,"time_end":131.87},{"position":41,"content":"So I could have one called 'Grandparents' for instance?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-16-test-2-part-1-2022-12-31-23-02-16/41.mp3","time_start":132.09,"time_end":136.29},{"position":42,"content":"Exactly.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-16-test-2-part-1-2022-12-31-23-02-16/42.mp3","time_start":136.46,"time_end":137.59},{"position":43,"content":"And do you do anything besides scan the photos?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-16-test-2-part-1-2022-12-31-23-02-16/43.mp3","time_start":138.23,"time_end":142.21},{"position":44,"content":"Like, can you make any improvements?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-16-test-2-part-1-2022-12-31-23-02-16/44.mp3","time_start":142.37,"time_end":144.97},{"position":45,"content":"Yes, in the standard service each photo is checked,","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-16-test-2-part-1-2022-12-31-23-02-16/45.mp3","time_start":145.13,"time_end":149.53},{"position":46,"content":"and we can sometimes touch up the colour a bit, or improve the contrast -","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-16-test-2-part-1-2022-12-31-23-02-16/46.mp3","time_start":149.53,"time_end":154.36},{"position":47,"content":"that can make a big difference.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-16-test-2-part-1-2022-12-31-23-02-16/47.mp3","time_start":154.36,"time_end":156.26},{"position":48,"content":"OK.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-16-test-2-part-1-2022-12-31-23-02-16/48.mp3","time_start":156.45,"time_end":157.46},{"position":49,"content":"And some of the photos are actually quite fragile -","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-16-test-2-part-1-2022-12-31-23-02-16/49.mp3","time_start":157.57,"time_end":160.73},{"position":50,"content":"they won't get damaged in the process, will they?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-16-test-2-part-1-2022-12-31-23-02-16/50.mp3","time_start":160.9,"time_end":163.8},{"position":51,"content":"No, if any look particularly fragile, we'd do them by hand.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-16-test-2-part-1-2022-12-31-23-02-16/51.mp3","time_start":163.96,"time_end":168.71},{"position":52,"content":"We do realise how precious these old photos can be.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-16-test-2-part-1-2022-12-31-23-02-16/52.mp3","time_start":168.81,"time_end":172.06},{"position":53,"content":"Sure.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-16-test-2-part-1-2022-12-31-23-02-16/53.mp3","time_start":172.23,"time_end":173.11},{"position":54,"content":"And another thing is we can make changes to a photo if you want -","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-16-test-2-part-1-2022-12-31-23-02-16/54.mp3","time_start":173.24,"time_end":177.68},{"position":55,"content":"so if you want to remove an object from a photo,","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-16-test-2-part-1-2022-12-31-23-02-16/55.mp3","time_start":177.68,"time_end":181.27},{"position":56,"content":"or maybe alter the background, we can do that.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-16-test-2-part-1-2022-12-31-23-02-16/56.mp3","time_start":181.27,"time_end":184.91},{"position":57,"content":"Really?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-16-test-2-part-1-2022-12-31-23-02-16/57.mp3","time_start":184.91,"time_end":185.98},{"position":58,"content":"I might be interested in that.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-16-test-2-part-1-2022-12-31-23-02-16/58.mp3","time_start":186.25,"time_end":188.44},{"position":59,"content":"I'll have a look through the photos and see.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-16-test-2-part-1-2022-12-31-23-02-16/59.mp3","time_start":188.66,"time_end":191.46},{"position":60,"content":"Oh, and talking of fixing photos -","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-16-test-2-part-1-2022-12-31-23-02-16/60.mp3","time_start":191.96,"time_end":194.96},{"position":61,"content":"I've got a few that aren't properly in focus.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-16-test-2-part-1-2022-12-31-23-02-16/61.mp3","time_start":194.96,"time_end":198.03},{"position":62,"content":"Can you do anything to make that better?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-16-test-2-part-1-2022-12-31-23-02-16/62.mp3","time_start":198.13,"time_end":200.66},{"position":63,"content":"No, I'm afraid that's one thing we can't do.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-16-test-2-part-1-2022-12-31-23-02-16/63.mp3","time_start":200.77,"time_end":204.07},{"position":64,"content":"OK.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-16-test-2-part-1-2022-12-31-23-02-16/64.mp3","time_start":204.2,"time_end":205.23},{"position":65,"content":"Any other information I can give you?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-16-test-2-part-1-2022-12-31-23-02-16/65.mp3","time_start":205.39,"time_end":207.67},{"position":66,"content":"...oh, how long will it all take?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-16-test-2-part-1-2022-12-31-23-02-16/66.mp3","time_start":209.54,"time_end":212.0},{"position":67,"content":"We aim to get the copying done in ten days.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-16-test-2-part-1-2022-12-31-23-02-16/67.mp3","time_start":212.0,"time_end":215.04},{"position":68,"content":"Fine.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-16-test-2-part-1-2022-12-31-23-02-16/68.mp3","time_start":215.18,"time_end":216.21},{"position":69,"content":"Right, well I'll get the photos packed up in a box and post them off to you.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-16-test-2-part-1-2022-12-31-23-02-16/69.mp3","time_start":216.4,"time_end":221.72},{"position":70,"content":"Right. If you've got a strong cardboard box, that's best.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-16-test-2-part-1-2022-12-31-23-02-16/70.mp3","time_start":221.74,"time_end":226.03},{"position":71,"content":"We've found that plastic ones sometimes break in the post.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-16-test-2-part-1-2022-12-31-23-02-16/71.mp3","time_start":226.03,"time_end":229.92},{"position":72,"content":"OK.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-16-test-2-part-1-2022-12-31-23-02-16/72.mp3","time_start":230.11,"time_end":231.09},{"position":73,"content":"Right, thanks for your help. Bye.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-16-test-2-part-1-2022-12-31-23-02-16/73.mp3","time_start":231.53,"time_end":234.72},{"position":74,"content":"Bye.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-16-test-2-part-1-2022-12-31-23-02-16/74.mp3","time_start":234.93,"time_end":235.8}]}